<br>
::As they walked into the main hall, before them was a long table.  On this table was various fruits, roasts, meats, and almost any food imaginable, including the infamous Ambrosia::<br>
<br>
::Hades escorted Persephone to the head of the table, where two chairs with high backs were next to each other.  One was slightly higher than the other::<br>
<br>
::Hades then took Persephone's hand and stood in front of their chairs.  Hades sat down in the chair with the higher back.  He nodded for Persephone to take her seat beside him.  With that Hades reached over the table and grabbed a pomegranite.  He tore it open and started eating some of the juicy seeds within.  A little bit of the juice dribbled on his lip as he smiled to Persephone::<br>
<br>
::Along the long table, were various other empty chairs.  These, were put for any other gods that may come by, as this was welcome.  For Hades this is a happy occasion...the return of his Queen.  All those who wished to celebrate along with them, were more than welcome, particularly those gods of the Underworld.  Olympians were welcome to celebrate as well, though he knew no sane one would willingly come to the Underworld::<br>
<br>
&quot;Eat up, my Queen. I'm sure your journey has hungered you, as it has hungered me&quot;  ::As a shade floated over and began filling her plate for her:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hypnos@amazonsunite>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://glyphs.com/art/fractals/images/hypnos.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 327<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(12/20/02 7:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=283.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> dropping in for a visit</span><hr size=1> ***In a swirl of black smoke and blue light, Hypnos appears sitting in one of the chairs. A fragrance of jasmine, cardamon, and orange blossom fills the air around him. He wore a dark blue garment, cape, and had a tattoo of hindu on his cheek, but he quickly pealed it off his skin as if it were nothing... Once again his look had changed as he had spent about a month in India or the territory of the Aryians. There he spend some time with the Hindu gods, but spent the most time with Shiva and Brahma.*** <br>
