<br>
::Jumping out of her seat, she quickly runs over to him jumping into his arms while burying her face between his neck and right shoulder sniffing happily:: I have missed you my good friend. You've been to India! And you smell of their sweet scent! I would grow their flowers down here but I don't know how, it is so complex. Oh how I wish I could have those perfumes with those wonderful jasmines and orange blossoms down here with me ::Her lower lips pouts out as she looks at him enviously:: <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. faithful wife to Hades... princesss goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixlordhadesxi>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/6/03 10:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=283.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: An old friend</span><hr size=1> ::Hades sat back and watched Persephone get up and embrace Hypnos as a hug.  After the exchange and the point, Hades simply looked at her::<br>
<br>
&quot;I told you a long time ago...if you can grow it in your private gardent...you can grow it down here.&quot;<br>
